INSERT INTO DEMOGRAPHIC_TIME (ID, BEGIN_DATE, END_DATE, MONTH, MONTH_INT, QUARTER, YEAR, YEAR_INT) SELECT TO_NUMBER (TO_CHAR(ADD_MONTHS(:ETLFORSELECTEDPROVIDER.DEMOGRAPHIC_TIME_START,(LEVEL-1)),'YYYYQMM')) ID,
ADD_MONTHS(:ETLFORSELECTEDPROVIDER.DEMOGRAPHIC_TIME_START,(LEVEL-1)) MONTH_BEGIN_DATE, LAST_DAY( ADD_MONTHS(:ETLFORSELECTEDPROVIDER.DEMOGRAPHIC_TIME_START,(LEVEL-1)) ) MONTH_END_DATE,
TO_CHAR( ADD_MONTHS(:ETLFORSELECTEDPROVIDER.DEMOGRAPHIC_TIME_START,(LEVEL-1)),'MON' ) MONTH , TO_NUMBER( TO_CHAR(ADD_MONTHS(:ETLFORSELECTEDPROVIDER.DEMOGRAPHIC_TIME_START,(LEVEL-1)),'MM')) MONTH_INT,
TO_CHAR(ADD_MONTHS(:ETLFORSELECTEDPROVIDER.DEMOGRAPHIC_TIME_START,(LEVEL-1)),'q') QUARTER, TO_CHAR(ADD_MONTHS(:ETLFORSELECTEDPROVIDER.DEMOGRAPHIC_TIME_START,(LEVEL-1)),'YYYY') YEAR, TO_NUMBER(TO_CHAR(ADD_MONTHS(:ETLFORSELECTEDPROVIDER.DEMOGRAPHIC_TIME_START,(LEVEL-1)),'YYYY')) YEAR_INT
FROM DUAL CONNECT BY ( LEVEL - 1 ) <= MONTHS_BETWEEN (:ETLFORSELECTEDPROVIDER.SYSDATE, :ETLFORSELECTEDPROVIDER.DEMOGRAPHIC_TIME_START)

INSERT INTO DEMOGRAPHIC_TIME (ID, BEGIN_DATE, END_DATE, MONTH, MONTH_INT, QUARTER, YEAR, YEAR_INT) SELECT TO_NUMBER (TO_CHAR(ADD_MONTHS(:ETLFORSELECTEDPROVIDER.DEMOGRAPHIC_TIME_START,(LEVEL-1)*3),'YYYYQ')) ID,
ADD_MONTHS(:ETLFORSELECTEDPROVIDER.DEMOGRAPHIC_TIME_START,(LEVEL-1)*3) QUARTER_BEGIN_DATE,
CASE WHEN TO_CHAR(:ETLFORSELECTEDPROVIDER.SYSDATE, 'YYYYQ') = TO_CHAR(LAST_DAY(ADD_MONTHS(:ETLFORSELECTEDPROVIDER.DEMOGRAPHIC_TIME_START,(LEVEL-1)*3 + 2) ), 'YYYYQ') THEN TRUNC(LAST_DAY (:ETLFORSELECTEDPROVIDER.SYSDATE)) ELSE LAST_DAY( ADD_MONTHS(:ETLFORSELECTEDPROVIDER.DEMOGRAPHIC_TIME_START,(LEVEL-1)*3 + 2) ) END QUARTER_END_DATE,
'N/A' MONTH , -1 MONTH_INT,
TO_CHAR(ADD_MONTHS(:ETLFORSELECTEDPROVIDER.DEMOGRAPHIC_TIME_START,(LEVEL-1)*3),'q') QUARTER, TO_CHAR(ADD_MONTHS(:ETLFORSELECTEDPROVIDER.DEMOGRAPHIC_TIME_START,(LEVEL-1)*3),'YYYY') YEAR, TO_NUMBER(TO_CHAR(ADD_MONTHS(:ETLFORSELECTEDPROVIDER.DEMOGRAPHIC_TIME_START,(LEVEL-1)*3),'YYYY')) YEAR_INT
FROM DUAL CONNECT BY ( LEVEL - 1 ) <= MONTHS_BETWEEN (:ETLFORSELECTEDPROVIDER.SYSDATE, :ETLFORSELECTEDPROVIDER.DEMOGRAPHIC_TIME_START)/3

INSERT INTO DEMOGRAPHIC_TIME (ID, BEGIN_DATE, END_DATE, MONTH, MONTH_INT, QUARTER, YEAR, YEAR_INT) SELECT TO_NUMBER (TO_CHAR(ADD_MONTHS(:ETLFORSELECTEDPROVIDER.DEMOGRAPHIC_TIME_START,(LEVEL-1)*12),'YYYY')) ID,
ADD_MONTHS(:ETLFORSELECTEDPROVIDER.DEMOGRAPHIC_TIME_START,(LEVEL-1)*12) YEAR_BEGIN_DATE,
CASE WHEN EXTRACT (YEAR FROM :ETLFORSELECTEDPROVIDER.SYSDATE) = EXTRACT ( YEAR FROM LAST_DAY(ADD_MONTHS(:ETLFORSELECTEDPROVIDER.DEMOGRAPHIC_TIME_START,(LEVEL-1)*12 + 11) )) THEN TRUNC(LAST_DAY (:ETLFORSELECTEDPROVIDER.SYSDATE)) ELSE LAST_DAY( ADD_MONTHS(:ETLFORSELECTEDPROVIDER.DEMOGRAPHIC_TIME_START,(LEVEL-1)*12 + 11) ) END YEAR_END_DATE,
'N/A' MONTH , -1 MONTH_INT, -1 QUARTER,
TO_CHAR(ADD_MONTHS(:ETLFORSELECTEDPROVIDER.DEMOGRAPHIC_TIME_START,(LEVEL-1)*12),'YYYY') YEAR, TO_NUMBER(TO_CHAR(ADD_MONTHS(:ETLFORSELECTEDPROVIDER.DEMOGRAPHIC_TIME_START,(LEVEL-1)*12),'YYYY')) YEAR_INT
FROM DUAL CONNECT BY ( LEVEL - 1 ) <= MONTHS_BETWEEN (:ETLFORSELECTEDPROVIDER.SYSDATE, :ETLFORSELECTEDPROVIDER.DEMOGRAPHIC_TIME_START)/12
